          <button type="button" class="btn btn-link search-open nav-btn-link position-relative">
            
            <div>
              <i class="bi bi-search nav-icon"></i>
            </div>  

            <div class="ml-20"></div>

          </button>

 <i class="bi bi-x nav-icon"></i> 

in this if slideDown then change  <i class="bi bi-search nav-icon"></i> to  <i class="bi bi-x nav-icon"></i>  with fade effect and if slideUp  then change <i class="bi bi-x nav-icon"></i>   to <i class="bi bi-search nav-icon"></i> <i class="bi bi-x nav-icon"></i> 
